<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the {{Zend_Http_UserAgent_AbstractDevice}} class, on line 557, it is assumed that array key {{3}} exists in the array named {{$comment}}.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
    $result['browser_language'] = trim($comment[3]);
</code></pre>

<p>I propose it should be as follows:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (isset($comment[3])) {
    $result['browser_language'] = trim($comment[3]);
}
</code></pre>

<p>An alternative would be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (array_key_exists(3, $comment[3])) {
    $result['browser_language'] = trim($comment[3]);
}
</code></pre>

